"{\"uid\": \"thestar.com.my-news-world-2024-07-28-olympics--australia-wins-women039s-4x100m-freestyle-relay-gold-updated\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Sunday, 28 Jul 2024  PARIS, July 27 (Xinhua) -- Australia set a new Olympic record as it claimed its fourth consecutive gold medal in the women's 4x100m freestyle relay at the Paris 2024 Games on Saturday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 205, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 37, \"end\": 43, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\", \"score\": 0.9999999645478972, \"rank\": 3.545058480888463e-08, \"text\": \"Xinhua\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Australian team of Mollie O'Callaghan, Shayna Jack, Emma McKeon and Meg Harris finished in three minutes and 28.92 seconds, beating its own previous Olympic record of 3:29.69 set in Tokyo three years ago.\", \"from\": 207, \"to\": 415, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 207, \"end\": 221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9066977798196878e-14, \"text\": \"The Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\"}, {\"begin\": 211, \"end\": 226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_speedway_team\", \"score\": 0.896051721927967, \"rank\": 0.05916577257715136, \"text\": \"Australian team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_speedway_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_speedway_team\"}, {\"begin\": 230, \"end\": 248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mollie_O'Callaghan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mollie O'Callaghan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mollie_O'Callaghan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mollie_O'Callaghan\"}, {\"begin\": 250, \"end\": 261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shayna_Jack\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shayna Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shayna_Jack\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shayna_Jack\"}, {\"begin\": 263, \"end\": 274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma McKeon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\"}, {\"begin\": 279, \"end\": 289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meg_Harris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Meg Harris\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meg_Harris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meg_Harris\"}, {\"begin\": 393, \"end\": 398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.8680757028813708, \"rank\": 0.15196859399561055, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The United States were second at the Paris La Defense Arena in 3:30.20 and China third in 3:30.30.\", \"from\": 417, \"to\": 515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 421, \"end\": 434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9691915408848144, \"rank\": 0.01655773383959491, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 492, \"end\": 497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9371832758730723, \"rank\": 0.04985671998010881, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me it's definitely about getting up there and doing my country proud,\\\" said Jack, who missed out on the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 641, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a really special moment to stand on the podium with the other three girls, and represent the other two girls from our heat swim, I am really proud of myself and how far I have come, but I definitely missed that opportunity in 2021.\\\"\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 881, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 25-year-old from Brisbane paid tribute to her family and friends, many of whom were watching from the bleachers.\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 999, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 904, \"end\": 912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Gabba\", \"score\": 0.6187613556931417, \"rank\": 0.3905796311540613, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Gabba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Gabba\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There are so many people I would dedicate this to: to my parents who are in the stands and my partner Joel.\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's here tonight too, which is really special.\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1157, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no word for the amount of support they have given me up to this point and I am immensely grateful.\\\"\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1266, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia has won gold in the event at four of the past five Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\